\fs36 \cf0 Case Study: Revolutionizing Multi-interface UX @ Xerox\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\fs28 \cf0 Overview\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 As part of Xerox\'92s Experience Design Group, I helped transform the user experience of their ConnectKey-enabled multifunction printers (MFPs), driving both innovation and efficiency. This project was a significant milestone in my early career, where I introduced rapid prototyping and documentation-driven collaboration in an environment resistant to change. These initiatives streamlined processes, fostered consensus, and elevated product usability to new heights.\
This case study highlights how I overcame resistance, implemented modern UX methodologies, and unified stakeholders across geographies to deliver industry-leading results.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

