\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 Medical Staffing Brand\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 The competitive analysis revealed the following actionable insights:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls112\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Demographics:
\f1\b0  The primary audience skewed younger than the national average for healthcare workers, with a majority being women of color. This shaped the app\'92s design to be inclusive, supportive, and approachable.\
\ls112\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Market Gaps:
\f1\b0  Competitors often lacked clarity in job listings and user engagement, particularly for temporary and travel nursing roles. To address this, the app prioritized transparent pay rates, detailed job information, and intuitive navigation.\
\ls112\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Strategic Positioning:
\f1\b0  The brand was positioned as a 
\f0\b trusted partner
\f1\b0  for healthcare workers, focusing on advocacy, career growth, and flexibility. The branding should emphasized simplicity, empathy, and trust.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \strokec2 These insights guided the creation of 
\f0\b mood boards
\f1\b0  that represented potential visual directions. By gathering feedback on the mood boards, we achieved stakeholders alignment on a cohesive visual style that emphasized 
\f0\b reliability and approachability
\f1\b0 . The final brand style integrated elements that conveyed empathy while maintaining professionalism.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

