\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls113\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Demographics:
\f1\b0  The audience was diverse in terms of age, gender, and experience level, prompting design decisions that catered to a broader user base with straightforward, accessible interfaces.\
\ls113\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Market Strategy:
\f1\b0  The app prioritized rapid job placements, compliance management, and efficient onboarding to address competitive gaps.\
\ls113\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
