\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 \strokec2 Context\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Wae allows employers to schedule jobs ranging in length from a filling a single shift to applying for a long-term job that will include evaluation and interview processes before acceptance. Currently, the Careerstart staffing team uses Bullhorn as their primary CMS, with other dependences in other systems. An MVP version of job posting was developed, and we are iterating to improve.\
